signatureAbility.signatureDescription: Successful quarterbacks stay cool and stand confidently against the blitz. When they enter the zone, all blitzing linebackers and defensive backs are highlighted after the snap.
Passers with this ability are faster and more responsive to user input while scrambling behind the line of scrimmage.
Midway through the fourth quarter in close games, players with this ability can easily enter (and remain in) the Zone.
Passers with this ability have perfect accuracy on all throws while running outside the pocket (except on high/low throws).
While in the pocket, passers with this ability are almost guaranteed to evade the first sack attempt by a blitzing defensive back.
Receivers with this ability have an increased success rate when running double moves against man coverage.
When in the red zone, receivers with this ability have a better chance to win contested catches against single coverage.
Ballcarriers with this ability have more powerful stiff arm animations.
Ballcarriers with this ability receive better blocking on outside zone plays.
Blockers with this ability reduce a pass rusher's chances of using a quick block shed move.
Defenders with this ability are rarely faked out by ballcarrier moves (and cannot be faked out when user-controlled).
Defenders with this ability have higher chance to catch uncontested interceptions, and they have unlimited stamina on the return (until using a special move or breaking a tackle).
